INSERT INTO `comment_replies` (`reply_id`, `comment_id`, `reply_name`, `reply_content`, `created_at`) VALUES
(1, 19, 'Holly Golightly', 'You’re welcome Katniss. I crossed the border by ferry from Egypt to Jordan. I think the port was called Nuweiba. It was a pretty smooth process. That’s all the experience I have traveling between the two.', '2023-06-19 10:19:48'),
(2, 20, 'Holly Golightly', 'Hi Ariahna,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn Jordan safety shouldn’t be an issue as it is one of the safest countries in the region.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1: Unfortunately I can’t advise you out of experience in this but I would have a look at Viator as it has many reviews.<br />\r\nI would however recommend staying a night in Petra to have it all to yourself in the morning! Day trips all arrive at the same moment meaning it will be busy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2: I stayed at an Ibis. Close to some nice restaurants! There is only one Ibis.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI hope this helps and you can enjoy Jordan soon!', '2023-06-19 10:58:55'),
(3, 23, 'Katniss Everdeen', 'There’s something so relaxing about a long slow train journey. Haven’t really done it in India but I’m sure it would be amazing as well.', '2023-06-19 11:02:16'),
(4, 22, 'Katniss Everdeen', 'That sounds like an excellent plan. It is a very relaxing and chilled country to visit. And there were no better moments than those sat on the train. Thanks for your comment.', '2023-06-19 11:03:30'),
(5, 21, 'Katniss Everdeen', 'A train ride in Sri Lanka is a very popular thing to do. For good reason, it’s a fantastic experience.', '2023-06-19 11:04:26'),
(6, 25, 'Elizabeth Bennet', 'Yes, those hills can be a bit of a workout. I think it was punishment for all those Portuguese tarts I consumed.', '2023-06-19 18:22:36'),
(7, 17, 'Elizabeth Bennet', 'Glad to hear it. Good luck planning the trip – I’m sure you’ll have a great time. There’s so much variety in Lisbon which makes it such a great place to visit.', '2023-06-19 18:25:02'),
(8, 27, 'Satine Noir', 'Completely agree. I have been many times and always find something different and interesting to do. A truly great city.', '2023-06-19 18:32:53'),
(9, 28, 'Satine Noir', 'Thanks a lot. Hope you get the chance to go soon. It’s a great city.', '2023-06-19 18:38:38'),
(10, 26, 'Alex Megos', 'Paris is such a wonderful city, I have visited the city so many times, yet I never feel I have seen it all. I would love to go back again.', '2023-06-19 18:42:27'),
(11, 29, 'Elizabeth Bennet', 'There’s so much to see and it’s such a different world. Hope you get the chance to visit soon.', '2023-06-19 18:46:29');

